        <description><![CDATA[<p>定点観測。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9583.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9583.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9583.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9583.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9583"/></a></p>

